{"tid":1657731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（求教）林鄭個按揭政策喺為咗安撫收成期？","createTime":"2019-10-16T08:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T08:30:06.000Z","uid":174322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9c942a60a902d225c2cf520aa4ac510634a1e0a","tid":1657731,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"見好似好多人屌林鄭弱智，推個9成按揭貸款俾人上樓<br />\n但眾所鳩知，條垃圾啲政策從來都唔係為咗香港人訂嘅<br />\n<br />\n所以細佬諗咗陣反而覺得個政策其實喺咪想<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />製造樓市需求會增加嘅印象<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />穩住樓價<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />令到中產冇咁大意慾走資<br />\n<br />\n而背底係咪代表住真係有好一大班人靜靜地走緊資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影響緊成班收成期嘅直接利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以尋日陳建波出黎大大聲屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係咪真係代表緊我地㩜炒成功緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時間令人上樓除咗令佢唔敢再出黎<br />\n更加係縛死多啲人嘅資產<br />\n令領導可以喺支爆前走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：咩都唔識，純粹9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錯講俾個po 沉咗去算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8e6f6357d83ac4785149465fbf4720925455af","tid":1657731,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"83fa2034046b51d276b23b98b5fbe3877d5c1cb7","tid":1657731,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"傻啦<br />\n明知經濟差,要夾高個市<br />\n等領導先行<br />\n由始至終都唔係諗住幫你哋上車"},{"pid":"99c679a822b45ca3ba1f929691cfc1908bd96d72","tid":1657731,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83fa2034046b51d276b23b98b5fbe3877d5c1cb7","tid":1657731,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"傻啦<br />\n明知經濟差,要夾高個市<br />\n等領導先行<br />\n由始至終都唔係諗住幫你哋上車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:30:06.000Z","msg":"連中產都係condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但多口問多句，師兄會點建釋「點解領導咁多個月都未走到資」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇完文諗唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：無產on9仔"}]}